Interface TrafficLightNetwork

All Superinterfaces:
Agent, TrafficAgent
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractTrafficLightNetwork, PeakAwareTLN, RegularTLN
public interface TrafficLightNetwork
extends TrafficAgent

Traffic light network agent. Traffic Light Network it is a system of coordinated traffic lights on a particular road node, that expose coordinated behavior, for example, they all may obey one signal switching schedule.
